<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA64">
<l>nilāvilaṅku veṇmatiyai nēṭikkoḷ vāṉpō</l>
<l>lulāvi yuḻitarumā kollō - nilāvirunta</l>
<l>cekkarav vāṉamē yokkun tirumuṭikkē</l>
<l>pukkaravaṅ kālaiyē pōṉṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As if to seek for himself the white moon shining with light,</l>
<l>will it roam [and] wander about, the snake, resembling the wind,</l>
<l>entering to the sacred crown that resembles the beautiful sky</l>
<l>of the evening where there is moonlight?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
